### API Versioning & Metrics: Drill 8

### 1. Request to V1
GET http://localhost:3007/v1/tasks

### 2. Request to V2
GET http://localhost:3007/v2/tasks

### 3. Generate success metrics (several calls)
GET http://localhost:3007/v1/tasks
GET http://localhost:3007/v2/tasks

### 4. Generate error metrics
GET http://localhost:3007/v1/error

### 5. Check metrics endpoint
GET http://localhost:3007/metrics
